---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Accomplishments - The10 Youth Excellence Center">
  <section class="accomplishments-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="section-label">OUR JOURNEY</span>
        <h1>Accomplishments</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Celebrating milestones, community impact, and the incredible journey of 
          empowering youth through yoga, service, and excellence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="timeline">
        <!-- 2025 Accomplishments -->
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">1</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">January 2025</div>
            <h3>USAYoga'25 National Qualifier Success</h3>
            <p>The10YEC youth participation in USAYoga'25 National Qualifier with Shouryan, Samhitha, Arshi, Radhika, and Kiran. All youth performed exceptionally and qualified for Nationals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">2</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">February 2025</div>
            <h3>Shivarathri: New Yoga Dance Flow</h3>
            <p>Nagastuthi performance featuring Sounds of Isha, showcasing our integration of traditional spirituality with modern movement.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">3</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">February 2025</div>
            <h3>USAYoga National Qualifier - Bay Area</h3>
            <p>Srini Gurrapu placed 3rd in Men's 50+ category, demonstrating excellence in yoga asanas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">4</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">March 18, 2025</div>
            <h3>Sankara Eye Foundation Yoga + Walkathon</h3>
            <p>Platinum Sponsor ($2,500 USD). Shouryan, Samhitha, Vedanshi, Kiran, and Anitha led our booth and yoga session. This marked our first booth presence with The10YEC standee.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">5</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">March 23, 2025</div>
            <h3>Yoga Foundation Camp</h3>
            <p>The10YEC Yoga Foundation Camp in partnership with Dharma Jagruthi Foundation, expanding our reach in community yoga education.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">6</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">March 30, 2025</div>
            <h3>Richwoods Ugadi Festival</h3>
            <p>The10YEC Yoga Dance Flow collaboration with "Presto Music Minds" Youth Band, celebrating cultural traditions through movement.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">7</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">April 5, 2025</div>
            <h3>Frisco Ramanavami Festival</h3>
            <p>Premiered our signature Yoga Dance Flow featuring Ramashtakam, blending devotional expression with yogic movement.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">8</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">May 2, 2025</div>
            <h3>USAYoga National Qualifier - Portsmouth, NH</h3>
            <p>Amrutha and Srini both qualified for nationals. Srini achieved 2nd place, demonstrating continued excellence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">9</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">June 19-21, 2025</div>
            <h3>EkaShri Schools of Yoga Retreat</h3>
            <p>Partnership with The10YEC and HUA, featuring Shriram Sarvotham ji and Eka ji. The10YEC contributed $10,000 USD to support this project and the mission to publish the YEC youth book.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item highlight">
          <div class="timeline-marker">10</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">June 2025</div>
            <h3>International Yoga Day Festival</h3>
            <p>Launch of The10YEC ventures. The ranch became an independent facility, and the new YEC Waters Edge Center was announced. Community partner event with all YEC ecosystem partners.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">11</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">July 2025</div>
            <h3>Education Support - Tirupathi, India</h3>
            <p>Supporting elementary school children in rural slums through execution partner EkamUSA. The10YEC provided $5,000 USD. Srini visited these centers in Tirupati.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">12</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">July 2025</div>
            <h3>PrathamUSA Partnership</h3>
            <p>Partnership with India's largest non-profit. The10YEC provided $5,000 USD to support "HamaraGao" for children in Warangal district, with commitment for additional $20,000. Funded through partner Basani Foundation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item highlight">
          <div class="timeline-marker">13</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">July 2025</div>
            <h3>USAYoga National Championship</h3>
            <p>Groundbreaking event in State College, PA with 7 representatives. The10YEC performed Ramashtakam Yoga Dance on the USA Yoga stage - first of its kind.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">14</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">September 2025</div>
            <h3>Swami Bodhananda Retreat</h3>
            <p>Partnership with Yoga Bharati at The10YEC ranch, bringing spiritual wisdom and yogic practices to the community.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">15</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">July 2025 - Ongoing</div>
            <h3>Yoga Bharati Partnership - Regular Classes</h3>
            <p>The10YEC partner Yoga Bharati launched yoga classes for kids, teens, and adults in 3 rooms every Saturday.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">16</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">August 2025</div>
            <h3>Yoga Bharati Residential Retreat</h3>
            <p>Hosted 4-night residential retreat for 14 kids and team, including Bhajan session at The10YEC ranch.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">17</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">October 2025</div>
            <h3>AUM Dallas Launch</h3>
            <p>Hosted AUM Dallas launch event at The10YEC, expanding our community partnerships and spiritual offerings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">18</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">November 2025</div>
            <h3>Nirvana - Buddha Performance</h3>
            <p>Collaboration with Utkala Dance Academy for "Nirvana - Buddha" Odissi Dance + Yoga dance performance. The10YEC contributed $250 through Basani Foundation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">19</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">November 2025</div>
            <h3>NrutyaShakti Dance Academy Collaboration</h3>
            <p>The10YEC provided $500 for this event and served as one of three chief guests for youth awards recognition.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">20</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">November 2025</div>
            <h3>New Yoga Flow: Kantara Brahmastala</h3>
            <p>Developed and premiered new innovative yoga flow sequence combining traditional and contemporary elements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">21</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">December 2025</div>
            <h3>Utkala Open House</h3>
            <p>Community engagement event showcasing our partnership and cultural integration efforts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">22</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-date">December 2025</div>
            <h3>Youth Podcast & Toastmasters Club Launch</h3>
            <p>Launched new youth podcast platform and Toastmasters club, empowering young voices and leadership development.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .accomplishments-hero {
    padding: 10rem 0 6rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, #F4A000 100%);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .accomplishments-hero h1 { 
    color: white; 
    margin: 1rem 0; 
  }
  
  .accomplishments-hero .section-label { 
    color: white; 
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle { 
    font-size: 1.3rem; 
    max-width: 800px; 
    margin: 0 auto; 
    opacity: 0.95; 
    color: white; 
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 3rem auto;
    padding-left: 60px;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 20px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--blue) 100%);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-left: 40px;
  }

  .timeline-item.highlight .timeline-content {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF9E6 0%, #FFECB3 100%);
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(244, 180, 26, 0.3);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .timeline-content {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-content:hover {
    transform: translateX(8px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .timeline-date {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }


  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline {
      padding-left: 40px;
    }

    .timeline::before {
      left: 10px;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      padding-left: 30px;
    }

    .timeline-marker {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .timeline-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .timeline-content h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
